      "comment": "ELIZA DAY (8) is a John Jeffrey-trained newcomer by Hooked On Scotch out of Ringbark Alice. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Strong market watch advised but profiles nicely for this. JIMARY BUTTERFLY (2) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish third, beaten 0.8 lengths, (16.79) at this track. Leading player again. MISS RAINMAKER (4) shows ability but remains a maiden after seven starts. Was below best last time when missed the frame finishing third (19.83) at this track. Expected to be in the finish again. YAMAZAKI CHASER (1) was unplaced here last start but gets his chance to atone.",
